{"msg":"返回成功","muban":[{"ename":"am","cunt":24,"grade":"1.0","cname":"A1/A2型题","shiti":[{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"Ⅱ型呼吸衰竭时不可能出现","discription":"呼吸衰竭的临床表现主要包括呼吸困难、发绀、神经精神症状、心血管系统症状及其他器官损害。其中呼吸困难是最早、最突出的症状表现，伴有二氧化碳潴留时，可出现呼吸频率及节律的变化，因此D、E均可出现。B、C均为心血管系统的症状，缺氧早期脑血流量增加，可出现搏动性急性头痛、头晕，其特征性的表现主要由二氧化碳潴留引起血管扩张所致；同时应表现为皮肤红润、湿暖多汗及球结膜水肿，因此A项错误，为本题答案。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_ve09001001j_am_1636_220815","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"头痛、头晕","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"球结膜水肿","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"呼吸深快","fourth":"神经精神症状","answerPic":"","first":"皮肤干燥"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"长期应用广谱抗生素可诱发哪种感染","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_ve09001001j_am_1644_220815","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"C","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"空肠弯曲菌感染","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"白色念珠菌感染","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"柯萨奇病毒感染","fourth":"轮状病毒感染","answerPic":"","first":"致病性大肠埃希菌感染"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"肺炎链球菌肺炎病人出现哪种表现提示有并发症发生","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_ve09001001j_am_1652_220815","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"胸痛","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"寒战、高热","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"口唇疱疹","fourth":"体温退后复升","answerPic":"","first":"咳铁锈色痰"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"呼吸衰竭病人最早、最突出的表现是","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_ve09001001j_am_1660_220815","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"呼吸困难","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"心率加快","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fift